## Limitations
The analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some sources may not fully capture the latest developments in economic policies related to pollution. Additionally, the complexity of economic systems means that the relationship between pollution and economic failure can vary significantly across different contexts and regions.

